WEBVTT

00:01:08.465 --> 00:01:09.865
I'm her ex-husband.

00:01:09.945 --> 00:01:12.145
Are you crazy?
My boss has never been married.

00:01:12.225 --> 00:01:13.905
Is IngIng your boss?

00:01:13.985 --> 00:01:15.865
I think it's possible
they're still together

00:01:15.945 --> 00:01:17.545
and trying to trick you.

00:01:17.625 --> 00:01:20.265
That's impossible.
Ing would never lie to me.

00:01:21.945 --> 00:01:24.745
You're so quick to pay me, huh?
Your new girlfriend must be rich.

00:01:24.825 --> 00:01:26.105
Ms. Lin has nothing to do with this.

00:01:26.625 --> 00:01:28.065
I'll get the money myself.

00:01:29.225 --> 00:01:30.505
How much do you want?

00:01:30.585 --> 00:01:32.145
It's him. I'm certain.

00:01:32.225 --> 00:01:35.385
I remember IngIng's ex-husband clearly.

00:01:41.185 --> 00:01:44.065
RECHARGE STATION

00:01:57.705 --> 00:01:59.825
Here's the brochure
for the new tutoring school,

00:01:59.905 --> 00:02:01.385
in case you're interested.

00:02:01.465 --> 00:02:02.985
Please register here.

00:02:03.065 --> 00:02:04.265
-Register here.
-Can I have one?

00:02:04.345 --> 00:02:05.865
-Hello.
-Thank you.

00:02:05.945 --> 00:02:08.905
This tutoring school will be opening here,
replacing Play Park.

00:02:08.985 --> 00:02:10.185
When will it open?

00:02:10.265 --> 00:02:12.145
At the end of this month
or early next month.

00:02:12.225 --> 00:02:13.785
If you're interested,
please feel free to register.

00:02:13.865 --> 00:02:15.065
-Okay.
-Yes.

00:02:15.145 --> 00:02:16.745
-Thank you.
-Please register here.

00:02:16.825 --> 00:02:18.745
-Here's the brochure. Hello.
-Yes.

00:02:18.825 --> 00:02:22.105
-Thank you.
-Please register here.

00:02:22.705 --> 00:02:23.745
-All done.
-Yes.

00:02:23.825 --> 00:02:26.585
-Can I scan to pay?
-Of course.

00:02:26.665 --> 00:02:28.465
-Go ahead.
-Okay, let me scan it.

00:02:28.545 --> 00:02:29.905
-Yes.
-Thank you.

00:02:29.985 --> 00:02:31.465
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

00:02:31.545 --> 00:02:33.985
-Can I scan too?
-Of course.

00:02:34.865 --> 00:02:36.385
Thank you.

00:02:48.905 --> 00:02:52.265
Why didn't you answer my call, Ms. Lin?

00:02:53.025 --> 00:02:55.465
I didn't hear it.
Maybe my phone was on silent.

00:02:56.585 --> 00:02:58.105
Ah.

00:02:59.145 --> 00:03:02.065
This is the list of students
who have registered.

00:03:02.705 --> 00:03:06.345
As for the money,
I've transferred it all to the company.

00:03:06.425 --> 00:03:09.025
And my commission

00:03:09.545 --> 00:03:11.585
is as we agreed.

00:03:13.185 --> 00:03:15.825
Would you like to wait for the monthly
total, or should I transfer it now?

00:03:17.265 --> 00:03:18.705
You can transfer it now.

00:03:25.545 --> 00:03:27.185
THAI QR PAYMENT

00:03:44.505 --> 00:03:45.705
Thank you.

00:03:47.705 --> 00:03:49.545
I think it's possible
they're still together

00:03:49.625 --> 00:03:50.905
and trying to trick you.

00:03:50.985 --> 00:03:53.825
That's impossible.
Ing would never lie to me.

00:03:53.905 --> 00:03:56.945
You never know, Ms. Lin.
Appearances can be misleading.

00:03:57.625 --> 00:04:00.065
And the two of you
haven't known each other

00:04:00.145 --> 00:04:01.505
that long, right?

00:04:02.105 --> 00:04:06.345
It's him. I'm certain.
I remember IngIng's ex-husband clearly.

00:04:06.865 --> 00:04:10.865
They must be working together.
You're being scammed, Ms. Lin.

00:04:14.465 --> 00:04:17.384
I'm trying to forget
everything that happened.

00:04:19.504 --> 00:04:22.865
I'm just telling myself
it was all a misunderstanding.

00:04:33.865 --> 00:04:35.105
I'm heading home now.

00:04:35.625 --> 00:04:37.145
Drive safely.

00:04:37.225 --> 00:04:39.225
Mm. See you later.

00:04:39.825 --> 00:04:41.025
Mm.

00:04:41.905 --> 00:04:43.185
Don't forget to miss me.

00:04:51.545 --> 00:04:52.905
Bye-bye.

00:05:05.025 --> 00:05:07.865
I won't push you for the truth

00:05:08.625 --> 00:05:11.745
because I'm afraid
I'll hear something I don't want to hear.

00:05:45.265 --> 00:05:46.625
How much is left?

00:05:48.985 --> 00:05:51.025
We still have time to find the rest.

00:05:51.785 --> 00:05:52.705
Want me to transfer it?

00:05:54.625 --> 00:05:55.705
No.

00:05:56.425 --> 00:06:00.265
Save your money.
This is my problem. I can handle it.

00:06:01.345 --> 00:06:02.545
Then…

00:06:04.745 --> 00:06:06.025
should we borrow from Ms. Lin?

00:06:08.425 --> 00:06:10.225
Drop that idea.

00:06:12.265 --> 00:06:13.745
I don't like it.

00:06:13.825 --> 00:06:15.185
Why not?

00:06:16.385 --> 00:06:18.505
We're just borrowing it.
We'll pay her back soon.

00:06:21.905 --> 00:06:23.025
She won't let us repay her.

00:06:26.225 --> 00:06:27.065
‎We need to believe
‎we can stand on our own.

00:06:28.785 --> 00:06:31.025
I don't want this
to turn into a debt of gratitude.

00:06:34.585 --> 00:06:36.785
She already feels bad enough for me.

00:06:40.745 --> 00:06:42.385
Okay, okay.

00:06:43.825 --> 00:06:46.065
Then I'll find a full-time job.

00:06:48.225 --> 00:06:50.185
It's my turn to support our family.

00:06:55.425 --> 00:06:57.505
That's great, bro.

00:06:59.345 --> 00:07:01.105
Let's see… how much is left?

00:07:02.025 --> 00:07:04.025
-Let me total it up again.
-Mm.

00:07:05.305 --> 00:07:07.985
SEPTEMBER'S EXPENSES

00:07:08.065 --> 00:07:11.105
LILIN

00:07:15.545 --> 00:07:16.825
Yes?

00:07:16.905 --> 00:07:19.785
I'm coming to pick you up.
Let's have lunch.

00:07:20.585 --> 00:07:23.785
I'm already out taking care of something.

00:07:23.865 --> 00:07:25.785
Maybe another time?

00:07:25.865 --> 00:07:27.665
Then we'll talk later.

00:07:28.185 --> 00:07:29.545
Okay.

00:07:32.425 --> 00:07:33.585
I'll be right back.

00:09:07.545 --> 00:09:09.905
LILIN FAMILYNEST SENT A PHOTO

00:09:24.465 --> 00:09:26.825
MS. LILIN

00:09:28.105 --> 00:09:29.425
Hello, Ms. Lin.

00:09:29.505 --> 00:09:32.185
Is that IngIng's ex-husband
in the photos I sent you?

00:09:32.265 --> 00:09:34.865
Yes, it's definitely him.

00:09:36.785 --> 00:09:38.465
How did you find him, Ms. Lin?

00:09:39.865 --> 00:09:41.625
I have to go. I'll tell you later.

00:09:53.385 --> 00:09:56.545
Look, look.

00:10:13.705 --> 00:10:14.785
Ms. Lin?

00:10:17.065 --> 00:10:18.785
Ing is out on business.

00:10:19.385 --> 00:10:21.065
You should've called first.

00:10:22.145 --> 00:10:23.705
I thought I'd surprise her.

00:10:25.225 --> 00:10:26.505
What's she out doing?

00:10:28.185 --> 00:10:30.585
I have no idea. I didn't ask.

00:10:31.665 --> 00:10:34.625
‎Ing has been taking on jobs lately.

00:10:34.705 --> 00:10:39.025
Yeah. IngIng seems so busy with work
that she hasn't had time to see me.

00:10:39.785 --> 00:10:42.665
Do you have an urgent need for money?

00:10:45.865 --> 00:10:49.905
If you're having problems, you can
always talk to me, Ith. Don't be shy.

00:10:53.265 --> 00:10:55.265
Are you keeping something from me?

00:10:58.705 --> 00:10:59.545
No.

00:11:01.065 --> 00:11:02.185
Actually…

00:11:04.185 --> 00:11:05.425
Ing wanted to…

00:11:06.225 --> 00:11:08.385
save money for Donut

00:11:08.905 --> 00:11:11.745
for when he starts school.

00:11:15.185 --> 00:11:16.265
Yeah.

00:11:18.265 --> 00:11:19.785
Let's go play. Okay?

00:11:19.865 --> 00:11:22.945
Come on. Let's go.

00:11:23.025 --> 00:11:25.545
Let's go play. Here.

00:11:49.545 --> 00:11:52.665
Please wait until the end of the month.
Don't change your mind yet.

00:11:53.265 --> 00:11:54.505
Call me when you're ready.

00:11:55.025 --> 00:11:56.065
Yes, sir.

00:11:57.505 --> 00:11:58.545
Goodbye.

00:12:03.225 --> 00:12:06.265
Satisfied now?
My car will definitely sell.

00:12:07.425 --> 00:12:08.465
Okay.

00:12:12.865 --> 00:12:14.105
Wait.

00:12:15.385 --> 00:12:16.265
Can you drop me off at the same place?

00:12:17.025 --> 00:12:18.145
There are plenty of taxis here.

00:12:18.665 --> 00:12:19.745
What?

00:12:43.145 --> 00:12:44.225
Here you go, ma'am.

00:12:52.665 --> 00:12:54.225
Ms. Lin, you have to stay firm.

00:12:54.305 --> 00:12:58.025
The evidence couldn't be clearer.
They're tricking you.

00:13:01.665 --> 00:13:04.985
Let me collect myself first,
then I'll talk to Ing.

00:13:06.625 --> 00:13:10.025
She won't admit it.
She probably already has an excuse ready.

00:13:10.105 --> 00:13:12.585
And you'll probably believe her again,
like you always do.

00:13:13.345 --> 00:13:15.345
Give me some time.

00:13:17.065 --> 00:13:20.305
It's best to move on quickly. Right now,

00:13:20.385 --> 00:13:22.585
a big responsibility is waiting for you.

00:13:26.985 --> 00:13:30.945
I learned that
your aunt is about to take over a factory.

00:13:31.025 --> 00:13:32.905
There's no time to waste.

00:13:46.105 --> 00:13:47.585
Hello, Tutor's dad.

00:13:47.665 --> 00:13:48.625
Right here, please.

00:13:48.705 --> 00:13:50.185
RECHARGE STATION

00:13:50.265 --> 00:13:51.745
Hello.

00:13:51.825 --> 00:13:53.545
Hello.

00:13:54.145 --> 00:13:56.425
-Oh, you're wearing sunglasses too.
-Thank you.

00:13:56.505 --> 00:13:58.065
Thank you.

00:14:00.585 --> 00:14:04.345
Hello. Please register here. Yes.

00:14:09.665 --> 00:14:12.105
Can a 60-year-old uncle sign up for this?

00:14:13.185 --> 00:14:14.345
Mr. Pao!

00:14:21.865 --> 00:14:22.985
-Mr. Pao.
-Hm?

00:14:24.905 --> 00:14:26.385
Well, well.

00:14:26.465 --> 00:14:29.185
Thought you weren't coming
to see us anymore.

00:14:29.785 --> 00:14:31.345
I had to come.

00:14:32.945 --> 00:14:36.225
But something's been bothering me.

00:14:36.985 --> 00:14:38.225
What is it?

00:14:38.745 --> 00:14:42.505
Ms. Lin's father called me.

00:14:44.025 --> 00:14:46.185
He was worried

00:14:46.865 --> 00:14:49.385
and asked me to find a way

00:14:49.465 --> 00:14:51.145
to close Play Park as soon as possible.

00:14:52.545 --> 00:14:53.665
And now

00:14:54.825 --> 00:14:58.785
there's trouble at my house,
and I need his help.

00:14:59.665 --> 00:15:03.385
But I don't have the courage to face him.

00:15:05.105 --> 00:15:06.665
I'm at my wits' end.

00:15:07.265 --> 00:15:10.865
Can you help me?

00:15:15.185 --> 00:15:19.185
We decided to postpone
Play Park's closure indefinitely.

00:15:22.265 --> 00:15:23.105
Manager!

00:15:27.705 --> 00:15:29.865
Ms. Lin, please be honest.

00:15:29.945 --> 00:15:33.545
Did you put off
Play Park's closing date indefinitely

00:15:34.945 --> 00:15:36.265
because of me?

00:15:37.305 --> 00:15:38.625
I feel really bad

00:15:41.585 --> 00:15:43.745
for causing trouble
between you and your father.

00:15:44.425 --> 00:15:46.425
Don't blame yourself.

00:15:47.745 --> 00:15:50.265
I didn't do it to please you.

00:15:52.345 --> 00:15:54.865
I really agree with your idea.

00:16:04.305 --> 00:16:05.585
I'll resign, Mr. Pao.

00:16:08.905 --> 00:16:10.785
It's probably for the best.

00:16:30.025 --> 00:16:33.865
Ms. Lin is attending a company seminar
in Pattaya for three days and two nights.

00:16:39.345 --> 00:16:40.865
Excuse me, sir.

00:16:44.705 --> 00:16:47.705
Ms. IngIng, the Play Park manager,
is here to see you.

00:16:47.785 --> 00:16:49.265
Shall I let her in?

00:16:54.505 --> 00:16:55.545
Let her in.

00:17:22.905 --> 00:17:25.224
Okay, what does Fifi look like?

00:17:25.305 --> 00:17:27.545
She has round eyes.

00:17:27.625 --> 00:17:28.825
Okay, round eyes.

00:18:08.865 --> 00:18:13.105
Are you free this afternoon? Can we meet?

00:18:14.465 --> 00:18:16.265
If you're not, that's okay.

00:18:57.705 --> 00:18:58.585
Have you been waiting long?

00:18:59.505 --> 00:19:00.545
I just got here too.

00:19:09.945 --> 00:19:11.665
Is there something
you wanted to talk about?

00:19:21.065 --> 00:19:24.985
Do you still want to attend the seminar
in Pattaya that I invited you to?

00:19:25.065 --> 00:19:26.905
Oh.

00:19:27.945 --> 00:19:29.425
I thought it was something else.

00:19:32.585 --> 00:19:33.545
I'll go.

00:19:34.745 --> 00:19:36.145
Let's go, let's go.

00:20:20.865 --> 00:20:22.505
How was that even a breakup, Ms. Lin?

00:20:22.585 --> 00:20:25.905
She lied to you so much,
and you're still going on a trip with her?

00:20:26.585 --> 00:20:29.905
Before it ends badly,
can't we at least have some good memories?

00:20:31.665 --> 00:20:34.025
I really don't understand you.

00:20:36.105 --> 00:20:39.905
Since I started dating Ing,
it's felt like a dream, Jane.

00:20:39.985 --> 00:20:41.865
I've been really happy.

00:20:46.825 --> 00:20:49.625
I don't know if I'll ever meet
someone like her again.

00:20:52.465 --> 00:20:53.665
You will.

00:20:53.745 --> 00:20:55.785
My Ms. Lin is lucky.

00:20:55.865 --> 00:20:57.945
You'll never meet a liar like that again.

00:20:58.545 --> 00:21:00.545
Please don't give in, Ms. Lin.

00:21:00.625 --> 00:21:03.905
You have to end this
and throw it into the sea.

00:21:04.825 --> 00:21:07.105
But I really love Ing.

00:21:08.745 --> 00:21:09.785
Love?

00:21:12.505 --> 00:21:16.265
If that's the case, you might as well
throw yourself into the sea too.

00:21:17.945 --> 00:21:19.305
‎Please excuse me.

00:21:20.025 --> 00:21:21.225
Oh?

00:21:21.305 --> 00:21:23.905
-Where are you going, Jane?
-To the beach.

00:21:23.985 --> 00:21:26.265
Come back. I still have more to say.

00:21:41.465 --> 00:21:43.185
Woohoo!

00:21:43.265 --> 00:21:45.865
Woohoo!

00:21:46.385 --> 00:21:48.425
-Hey, the diapers are here.
-Mm.

00:21:48.505 --> 00:21:49.825
The washed cloth diapers are here.

00:21:50.785 --> 00:21:52.305
How long will you be gone?

00:21:52.825 --> 00:21:54.465
-Three days and two nights.
-Yeah.

00:21:55.305 --> 00:21:57.505
Donut's supplies will last a month.

00:21:59.945 --> 00:22:02.825
Just go.
Don't keep your girlfriend waiting.

00:22:04.185 --> 00:22:09.625
You talk too much. Mama will be back soon.
Stay with Uncle Ith, okay?

00:22:09.705 --> 00:22:11.785
Be a good boy.

00:22:12.505 --> 00:22:14.505
Come here.

00:22:14.585 --> 00:22:16.185
You're getting heavier every day.

00:22:16.265 --> 00:22:17.265
Ugh.

00:22:18.225 --> 00:22:21.585
Have fun, sis.
And don't just stay in your room.

00:22:22.865 --> 00:22:24.025
I know.

00:22:26.025 --> 00:22:28.265
If anything comes up, call me anytime.

00:22:29.425 --> 00:22:31.745
Pattaya's just a phone call away, right?

00:22:31.825 --> 00:22:33.825
I'll be back before you know it.

00:22:33.905 --> 00:22:35.905
-Go.
-Yeah.

00:22:40.545 --> 00:22:42.225
-Bye-bye. Bye-bye.
-I'm heading out.

00:22:42.305 --> 00:22:44.065
-Bye-bye!
-Bye-bye.

00:22:44.145 --> 00:22:47.025
-Bye-bye.
-Bye-bye. Bye-bye.

00:22:47.625 --> 00:22:48.505
Bye-bye?

00:22:51.065 --> 00:22:52.785
Come on. Let's go see Mama off.

00:22:59.185 --> 00:23:00.345
-Donut!
-Come on, bye-bye.

00:23:00.425 --> 00:23:03.305
-Bye-bye!
-Bye-bye. Wave bye-bye.

00:23:03.385 --> 00:23:04.985
I'm going now.

00:23:08.625 --> 00:23:10.265
-I'm leaving now, Ith.
-Yeah.

00:23:10.345 --> 00:23:12.665
-Bye-bye. Let's go.
-Let's go.

00:23:12.745 --> 00:23:14.785
Ith, take good care of him for me.

00:23:15.345 --> 00:23:18.225
Look, Mama's leaving. Look at her. See?

00:23:19.465 --> 00:23:25.585
She's heading off now. Bye-bye.
Whoa, don't follow her.

00:23:26.505 --> 00:23:28.905
Come on. It's just you and me now.

00:23:29.945 --> 00:23:32.225
You're confused? Let's go inside.

00:23:38.145 --> 00:23:42.985
Mom said you're lovely
Dad said you're wonderful

00:23:43.065 --> 00:23:47.385
My siblings also said
That you're the one for me

00:23:47.465 --> 00:23:49.945
You take care of me tirelessly

00:23:50.025 --> 00:23:53.025
It'd be really hard not to love you

00:23:53.105 --> 00:23:56.665
Because everything about you
Ticks my boxes, ticks my boxes

00:23:56.745 --> 00:23:58.745
You tick all my boxes

00:25:02.345 --> 00:25:04.145
I don't see the beach anywhere.

00:25:05.865 --> 00:25:09.945
You said we were going to the beach.
Why are we at the Renaissance?

00:25:13.465 --> 00:25:14.345
Oh.

00:25:14.945 --> 00:25:17.025
And this is a double bed?

00:25:17.625 --> 00:25:18.745
Don't they have twin rooms?

00:25:19.785 --> 00:25:20.785
They're fully booked.

00:25:22.665 --> 00:25:23.825
That's such a classic excuse.

00:25:24.745 --> 00:25:25.865
Really.

00:25:33.785 --> 00:25:35.745
Did you bring a swimsuit?

00:25:38.105 --> 00:25:39.265
Let's go swimming.

00:25:40.745 --> 00:25:43.025
We can go tomorrow.
We still have two more nights.

00:25:43.705 --> 00:25:47.385
You might not feel like swimming tomorrow.
Let's go today.

00:25:49.985 --> 00:25:51.185
That's true.

00:25:51.265 --> 00:25:52.705
Let's get changed.

00:25:57.945 --> 00:26:01.025
Hurry up, let's go.

00:30:21.465 --> 00:30:25.945
I shouldn't keep secrets
from Ms. Lin, right?

00:30:27.385 --> 00:30:30.225
Should I tell her everything now?

00:30:33.905 --> 00:30:36.145
Should I just break up with her?

00:30:36.225 --> 00:30:39.265
Or should we slowly drift
into just being friends?

00:30:40.185 --> 00:30:41.465
What should I do?

00:30:58.065 --> 00:30:59.625
Are you okay, Ms. Lin?

00:31:02.025 --> 00:31:04.865
You've seemed distracted since we arrived.

00:31:06.345 --> 00:31:09.985
Oh, I just have some work on my mind.

00:31:13.145 --> 00:31:14.425
Mm.

00:31:14.505 --> 00:31:17.065
It's okay
if you don't think about other women.

00:31:24.945 --> 00:31:28.065
Then I'm going to bed.

00:31:29.105 --> 00:31:32.585
You can go ahead and sleep.
I'm not tired yet.

00:31:36.265 --> 00:31:37.745
Don't make me wait too long.

00:33:09.705 --> 00:33:12.825
Thank you.
Let's travel together again sometime.

00:33:17.705 --> 00:33:19.505
Do you want to go inside and rest?

00:33:20.345 --> 00:33:23.625
It's okay. I'll stop by Play Park
for a bit and then head home.

00:33:25.345 --> 00:33:27.585
Oh. Okay.

00:33:33.425 --> 00:33:34.905
Did you forget something?

00:34:01.745 --> 00:34:03.345
ENGINE START / STOP

00:34:24.585 --> 00:34:25.865
Oh?

00:34:32.585 --> 00:34:34.344
Are you heading to the seminar now?

00:34:34.945 --> 00:34:35.865
Yes.

00:34:41.065 --> 00:34:42.865
Do you need your luggage too?

00:34:43.945 --> 00:34:46.545
Oh, I'll be staying in a different room.

00:34:47.705 --> 00:34:50.385
Huh? Why?

00:34:51.025 --> 00:34:52.985
We have a small team meeting tonight,

00:34:53.505 --> 00:34:55.465
and I don't want to disturb you.

00:34:57.825 --> 00:34:58.705
Okay.

00:35:25.145 --> 00:35:29.345
Donut? Donut? Mama's home.

00:35:36.385 --> 00:35:37.505
Where is he?

00:35:44.465 --> 00:35:46.025
Is he upstairs?

00:36:04.665 --> 00:36:06.625
Ith, where's Donut?

00:36:08.465 --> 00:36:09.385
He's downstairs.

00:36:10.265 --> 00:36:11.785
Downstairs? He's not there.

00:36:11.865 --> 00:36:16.105
How could he not be there? I put him
to sleep, then I came up to take a shower.

00:36:19.945 --> 00:36:21.985
Where is he? He's not there.

00:37:17.225 --> 00:37:20.105
DEAR CUSTOMERS
PLAY PARK IS TEMPORARILY CLOSED

00:37:27.905 --> 00:37:29.225
Did you find him, sis?

00:37:29.945 --> 00:37:30.865
Did you find him?

00:37:31.425 --> 00:37:32.945
How could a baby
just disappear like that, Ith?

00:37:34.505 --> 00:37:36.545
I haven't gone anywhere since you left.

00:37:41.465 --> 00:37:44.385
When I came in, the gate was open.

00:37:47.225 --> 00:37:48.105
Or…

00:37:49.985 --> 00:37:51.505
could Donut have been kidnapped?

00:37:54.505 --> 00:37:56.065
Where's the stroller?

00:37:59.945 --> 00:38:02.265
Guy. It's Guy.

00:38:27.625 --> 00:38:29.425
No… Donut…

00:38:30.025 --> 00:38:31.065
Did he pick up?

00:38:35.425 --> 00:38:37.585
Who else could it be?

00:38:53.465 --> 00:38:54.865
Donut?

00:39:09.025 --> 00:39:10.585
He's with him.

00:39:11.105 --> 00:39:12.385
He's with him, Ith.

00:39:12.465 --> 00:39:13.625
It's okay.

00:39:14.865 --> 00:39:17.465
We'll find him. We'll find him soon.

00:39:39.825 --> 00:39:42.985
-Hello, Ms. Lin.
-Hello, Ms. Lin.

00:39:43.065 --> 00:39:45.345
Why is Play Park closed?
What repairs are being done?

00:39:46.785 --> 00:39:48.785
Didn't you order it to close?

00:39:49.465 --> 00:39:50.425
No.

00:39:51.065 --> 00:39:53.905
But Family Nest ordered the closure.

00:39:53.985 --> 00:39:55.625
How is that possible?

00:39:56.465 --> 00:39:57.625
I'll call IngIng.

00:39:57.705 --> 00:40:01.305
The manager already knew.
She resigned without telling us.

00:40:02.545 --> 00:40:04.385
-IngIng resigned?
-Yes.

00:40:14.505 --> 00:40:17.265
Ith. Ith.
Please don't tell Ms. Lin about this

00:40:17.865 --> 00:40:20.105
I know. You've told me a hundred times.

00:40:21.545 --> 00:40:22.705
LILIN

00:40:23.425 --> 00:40:24.385
Ms. Lin?

00:40:27.505 --> 00:40:28.385
What do we do?

00:40:31.545 --> 00:40:33.065
Hey, hey, Ing.

00:40:34.425 --> 00:40:36.065
MS. LIN, ING'S GIRLFRIEND

00:40:37.705 --> 00:40:40.305
-Ms. Lin is calling.
-Don't answer.

00:41:17.425 --> 00:41:19.705
Did you order Play Park
to be shut down, Dad?

00:41:22.865 --> 00:41:26.065
You shouldn't have interfered
with my responsibilities.

00:41:28.705 --> 00:41:32.225
Didn't your manager friend tell you?

00:41:35.865 --> 00:41:37.665
So Ing knew about this?

00:41:39.825 --> 00:41:42.945
Mr. Pao called and said she resigned.

00:41:43.465 --> 00:41:44.825
So she probably did know.

00:41:46.225 --> 00:41:49.585
Before you two went to Pattaya, she came

00:41:49.665 --> 00:41:52.265
to talk to me for a long time.
You can ask Jane.

00:41:53.305 --> 00:41:54.425
Yes, that's true.

00:41:55.785 --> 00:41:58.345
I also gave her some money
as a parting gesture.

00:41:59.665 --> 00:42:00.505
Did you…?

00:42:00.585 --> 00:42:02.585
I didn't throw the money at her.

00:42:03.865 --> 00:42:07.185
I saw that she had good intentions
and was willing to sacrifice for you.

00:42:08.185 --> 00:42:09.825
I didn't want her to struggle.

00:42:11.425 --> 00:42:15.225
She's the head of her family.
She has people to support, doesn't she?

00:42:17.985 --> 00:42:20.665
Are you keeping something from me?

00:42:20.745 --> 00:42:21.825
No.

00:42:23.465 --> 00:42:24.625
Actually…

00:42:26.545 --> 00:42:30.705
Ing wanted to save money for Donut

00:42:31.225 --> 00:42:34.065
for when he starts school.

00:42:40.865 --> 00:42:43.185
Jane, show Lin the transfer slip.

00:42:43.265 --> 00:42:44.625
Yes, sir.

00:42:46.745 --> 00:42:47.905
Here.

00:42:47.985 --> 00:42:50.305
TRANSFER COMPLETE

00:42:50.385 --> 00:42:52.505
I was afraid
she wouldn't accept the money,

00:42:52.585 --> 00:42:54.465
so I sent it through Mr. Pao.

00:42:56.425 --> 00:42:57.625
Lin,

00:42:58.545 --> 00:43:01.585
I've helped you through a difficult time.

00:43:02.505 --> 00:43:05.225
Now let's move forward
with the tutoring school wholeheartedly,

00:43:05.305 --> 00:43:07.345
without worrying about anyone else.

00:43:08.265 --> 00:43:10.225
I feel betrayed.

00:43:13.985 --> 00:43:17.025
Ms. Lin, things have come to this.

00:43:17.105 --> 00:43:19.385
I think you should focus on your work.

00:43:19.465 --> 00:43:21.025
You're breaking up with her anyway.

00:43:41.625 --> 00:43:43.225
How could you abandon Donut like this?

00:43:44.305 --> 00:43:46.105
Do you have any humanity left?

00:43:46.185 --> 00:43:48.105
You broke your promise.

00:43:49.345 --> 00:43:50.785
You used me.

00:43:50.865 --> 00:43:52.185
You're quite clever.

00:43:52.265 --> 00:43:54.305
If you were truly sincere with Lin,

00:43:54.905 --> 00:43:57.105
you should have helped me
from the beginning.

00:43:57.625 --> 00:43:59.785
So you made it easy
for Dad to shut down Play Park.

00:44:00.905 --> 00:44:03.465
Can you please reassure me

00:44:03.545 --> 00:44:06.145
that I didn't give my heart to a liar?

00:46:08.225 --> 00:46:11.025
Subtitle translation by:
Anan Pratchayakul